 | MEDIA          |   Physical Components      |    Signal
 |----------------|----------------------------|----------------------------------
 | copper calbe   |  -UTP/STP                  | Electromagnetic signal
 | (wired)        |  -coaxial                  |
 |                | - connectors               |
 |                | -NICs                      |
 |                | -Ports/-Interfaces         |
 |----------------|----------------------------|-------------------------------
 | Fibre cable    | -single-mode fiber         | 
 | (wired)        | -multimate fiber           | - a light pulse equals 1 
 |                | -connectors                | - no light pulse is 0
